name: Hyrule Warriors: Definitive Edition (ゼルダ無双 ハイラルオールスターズ DX)
comment:
Loads to Main Menu, but receive `Unhandeld Exception: CLR/System.DllNotFoundException
An exception of type 'System.DllNotFoundException' occurred in FFmpeg.AutoGen.dll but was not handled in user code: 'Unable to load DLL 'avcodec.58': The specified module could not be found.'`
